line_1: The pois'nous Creeper, and the changing Preke
line_2: The secret Caverns of the Ocean seek.

line_1: Vig'rous they quit the Rock, and own the real Preke.
line_2: No Vizard then, or mimick Form they seek;

line_1: And thus insults the Colour-changing Preke.
line_2: With scornful Smile the Lamprey seems to speak,
